Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}請往這邊看！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好可愛！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}很好 很好
