Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}為什麼兩個女高中生都環繞在野本身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}後宮狀態?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這什麼狀況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}話說 這女孩是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雖然想問問發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因為發生了那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我不敢直視瞳的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是你 我叫的是那邊的狩獵豹女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你要跟著我到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不做的話給我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}為了防止你做 我在監視你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果「獸獄剎」被毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我會被哥哥責備的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你明明是獸鬪士卻不知道我哥哥是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再說你一直喊著要幹 你腦子裡只有這個詞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}剛才也是如果你不在就幹上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要幹… 要做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:07.91,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也給我考慮一下時間和地點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「修羅場」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}該不會三個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:09.46,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你不也是 明明之前就想幹的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:11.04,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}才不會做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這是18禁遊戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}野本
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}給我適可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}為了向我們炫耀女孩子們圍繞著你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你在瞧不起我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是 就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那…那個 我已經要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}把小兔子扔進餓狼群裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你們以為我們會這麼輕易放你們回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你…你什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我們都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那兩個女高中生是現在流行的獸耳娘cosplayer吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}為了擺脫現在的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只能請你們穿上這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}誰管你啊 呆子 殺了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}欸？可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}讓我來給這個除了打鬥一無是處的新手傳授些處世之道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你沒什麼值得我學習的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那這種你也能做到？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}部分獸化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只獸化必要的部位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}以此減少消耗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你怎麼做到的 告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是首先…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要換好衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}說起來 把內褲還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}欸？ 這是我的戰利品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那麼我在外面等著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我又看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}野本氏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎麼感覺人增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}攝影部和電影部也很感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}野本 事到如今你不會說要中止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊 不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}看這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喵~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}的確輕鬆不少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就像把自行車的變速器調到最輕鬆的那檔一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}請擺個姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是的 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你說什麼擺個姿勢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}稍微翹起屁股那種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}請用尾巴把裙子再撩上去一些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}感覺好受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蜜獾是一種不僅膽子大而且好奇心旺盛的動物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因此不管面對什麼狀況都能靈活應對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這種事還挺開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我還是第一次見到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}瞳露出那種表情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是群無可救藥的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那種事就開心成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}明明你也很開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那…那是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好啦 我會教你很多其他在戰鬥中能起作用的技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要好好聽我說的話哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這個人很會駕馭瞳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你叫野本來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這孩子稍微借我一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「獸獄剎」結束之前你暫時不會被盯上的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要進哪家店坐坐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯…我想吃烤薄餅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「獸獄剎」？那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}本來還很擔心會發展成什麼狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}瞳也心情很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}暫時安…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:07:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喲 我們又見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這…這個人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那…那時候的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蜜獾沒和你在一起嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷歐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你這不是在嚇唬他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}退下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我失禮了 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我是三門財閥會長陽參的孫女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}三門陽湖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}野本殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}事態變得很嚴重了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}野本裕也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}請你拒絕參加「獸獄剎」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那個…那到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是一對一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而是兩人以上的獸鬪士混戰的殲滅戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}為什麼會這麼突然地開始了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在「獸獄剎」中戰敗就意味著死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}死？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}瞳要參加這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這是祠堂零一的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那個男人把「牙鬪」當成自己實驗成果的試驗場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妄圖把神聖公平的決戰之地私有化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我是絕對不會答應的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就算你對我說這些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我會轉告瞳的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是是否參加…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}看來你還不明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你也要參加哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「獸獄剎」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是以獸鬪士為棋子的現實棋局
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而移動棋子的玩家就是作為出資人的你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你的一個判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就將決定蜜獾的生死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你有覺悟參加這個和她性命攸關的遊戲了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}作為棋子的你的確很優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是如果玩家是個廢柴的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是無法在「獸獄剎」中勝出的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}果然還是應該另尋出資人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再申請參加會比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我說你有在聽我說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒事 那傢伙就行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蛤？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以說那種一無是處的廢柴…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:18.99,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}越是弱者越能分辨誰是強者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以那傢伙絕對不會反抗我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也就是說 我能夠隨心所欲地行動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蛤？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你剛才說什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那個…我想等問過瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果她說可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就和她一起參加…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就因為你的判斷失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}瞳說不定會死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}為什麼把選擇都交給別人做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可是如果我一個人妄下決定的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可能會被殺的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我們回去吧 雷歐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:09:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好的 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}原以為被那個祠堂看中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不可能只單純是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒想到就是個笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再和他廢話下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}恐怕我都會被傳染了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}小姐決斷英明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是這下也明確了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我要在「獸獄剎」裡親自擊敗蜜獾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你也要參加嗎 陽湖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}還不是怪爺爺太放縱祠堂了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那個男人打算把「牙鬪」占為己有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那我就陪他玩玩好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這次的「獸獄剎」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是測量那傢伙能力的試金石
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,（三門財閥總帥 三門集團會長 三門陽參）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:11:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不過面對連雷歐都無法抗衡的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你究竟打算運用什麼棋子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}無需擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我們將出動「城戶」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}看來這次的「獸獄剎」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}會比往常更加腥風血雨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}實在是感激不盡啊 祠堂局長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有了蜜獾助陣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}終於能夠滿足石田會長的期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可以說是勝利在望了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我們也會儘可能地提供支援
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}管理局的待遇改善當然也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}瞳 關於「獸獄剎」…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我要參加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你也給我參加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}非常感謝 瞳小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:56.02,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你也要參加吧 岡島
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因我的判斷而死…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我們能夠從這場廝殺倖存下來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:57.57,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:12:00.07,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「獸獄剎」是團體戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:02.61,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}獸鬪士要以隊伍的形式出場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是 「獸獄剎」需要三人一組
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也就是說我們還缺少一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是不解風情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}看來還真是看不慣那個祠堂的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我們的會長代理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喂 岡島
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你找到了第三個人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這些全都被拒絕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.62,0:12:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}以石田財團的財力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:13:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}徵聘有實力的獸鬪士應該不難
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可能是有人在暗地裡搗鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}暗地裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}恐怕是其他財團做的手腳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可登錄的截止日期就是明天了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}野本 你快想想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就算你對我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那就只要找這個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不隸屬於任何財團
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雖然也不喜歡戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.69,0:13:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這附近的獸人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「獸獄剎」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哎 女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不過應該和瞳一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}獸化之後就變得非常強吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是我只是隻兔子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雖然你確實很弱…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在牙鬪中連戰連敗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因為輸的太多 找不到出資人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}連比賽都出場不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這不是完全不行嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以你們還是另請高明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:14:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我們也有不能退讓的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}稻葉閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}請加入我們的隊伍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可是我真的派不上用場哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}稻葉小姐的力量是必須的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我的力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而且如果能在「獸獄剎」中勝出
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}稻葉小姐也會聲名大噪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}名聲…聲名兔起?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是勝出後名聲大噪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}還是失敗了身首異處的二選一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}身首異處…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}絕絕絕對不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}稻葉閣下 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}岡島 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喂 兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}別給我磨磨唧唧的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}給我參加
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你不參加我們也參加不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不要給祠堂先生添麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}兔子也有能做到的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}比如說當誘餌什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}誘餌…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}絕絕絕對不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我絕對不參加
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}稻葉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你們嚇唬她幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}野本 你去說服她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}失敗了就幹掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}總感覺我已經被調教完了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這個 請用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就算說讓我說服她…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.09,0:15:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}稻葉你為什麼要成為獸人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:15:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}明明看起來不擅長戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我從小就沒什麼長處
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}腦子不好使 學習和運動也很差
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}家人和朋友都把我當傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以得知有獸化適應性的時候 高興得跳起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但兔子就是戰鬥力為零的渣渣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}唯一能自豪的只有逃得快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣的我去參加「獸獄剎」也沒什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可…可是你看 我不也沒什麼長處
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但還是作為玩家出場了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什麼弱小 什麼沒意義 和這沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以說 我想正是弱小反而能做到一些事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 大概就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好像真是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:16:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我可以收下這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你設陷阱了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:05.62,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你這是幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}當兔子受到敵人攻擊時 會躲進自己挖的洞裡進行避難
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}請不要現在才挖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}稻葉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:30.73,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好痛好痛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}咦 不痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那是什麼血呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}難不成…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,（獸鬪士 角蜥蜴 岸本紅裡 ）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我讓其他和石田有關的獸鬪士退場了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}剩下的只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}角蜥蜴 與天敵對峙時從眼裡噴出血液擊退敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「刺血閃」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:17:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}速度好快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這下沒辦法逃走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不會吧 我這麼快都被追上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不 你跑得夠快了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只不過你的眼睛就是擺設
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蜜獾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不會讓你得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那傢伙眼睛會噴出東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}躲開就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}剛才的那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}淨使出些奇怪的花招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}說到底你們哺乳類也就那水準
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是贏不了爬蟲類擁有的各種攻擊手段的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:19:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我不管你是哪種獸人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}獠牙更鋒利者獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這就是「牙鬪」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就算是兔子也有做得到的事對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我想正是弱小反而能做到一些事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}兔子的左右耳朵能各自捕捉聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}像雷達一樣正確掌握聲音來源的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}她的正後方還有一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}做得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}瞳 稻葉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}她是角供的獸鬪士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}瞳 難道你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:20:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}笨蛋 沒有殺死她們 看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}姐...姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就當這事是小兔子做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不然就把你們倆做的事告訴祠堂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}當作是我打贏她們的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果知道我打架了會大事不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}稻葉還沒有登錄在「獸獄剎」的名單裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.53,0:20:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我還是第一次打贏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}曾經一次都沒贏過嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}野本先生 我要參加「獸獄剎」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要參加嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是的 怎麼說我打贏了角供的獸鬪士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好 要加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不勝感激
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:21:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你沒有把剛才的獸人殺掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有問題嗎 殺了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真的 我也收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣一來的費用就使用交給你的一億元
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}還有就是 聽說你和八菱的豪豬戰鬥過了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是 沒有置她於死地是正確的判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\p1\bord0\1a&80&\c&H00FFFFFF\pos(-156.61,151.705)\fad(0,700)}m 0 0 m 0 0 l 1296 0 l 1296 363 l 0 363
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H00908D85\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs30\an7\fad(0,700)}可能雖然只是尊重野本的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H00908D85\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs30\an7\fad(0,700)}不過下一次的牙鬪他也會成為玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H00908D85\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs30\an7\fad(0,700)}希望你能和他一起協力進入備戰狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H00908D85\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs30\an7\fad(0,700)}下一步的安排改日再聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不過 沒殺人也是多虧了這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好 野本 我們一起特訓準備「獸獄剎」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}現在開始嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.93,0:21:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}到公園去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不了 我又不戰鬥 而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.23,0:21:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}理由真多 聽我的 出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等等 瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}別這麼吵鬧 又沒有受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是 我就是傷員啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.33,0:23:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}指引我吧 小押繪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.71,0:23:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒有目的懶懶散散的跑步真開心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.09,0:23:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}完全體會不到你說的樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.13,0:23:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快看 超級古董的自動販賣機裡有沒見過的果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.39,0:23:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好棒 買到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.30,0:23:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如何 好喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}導蜜鳥為了引導蜜獾去蜜蜂巢穴 時刻都要引起蜜獾注意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.48,0:23:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在幹嘛 這可是課堂上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.61,0:23:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是 押繪並不是獸人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.69,0:23:50.15,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.66,0:23:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}定期報告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.78,0:23:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}石田財閥的獸鬪士全部確定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.58,0:23:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但戰力不成規模
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.33,0:24:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}此時 角供財閥拋開正式戰鬥 密謀殺害蜜獾
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.71,0:24:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\pos(621.333,468.733)\fad(00,0)}第四牙 都叫你退出了 渣渣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}下集「都叫你退出了 渣渣」 以上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:46.10,op-jp,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:51.82,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}混ざり合う叫びは静寂を切り裂く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:54.61,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}研ぎ澄ませる野生で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:57.45,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}勝者だけが繋ぐ明日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:01:00.28,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}鋭く磨いた牙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.37,0:01:03.08,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}噛み付くその狂気
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:07.25,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}立ち向かおうか？戦いにわけなどいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:10.13,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}強さ求めるだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:25.43,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}螺旋に繋がれた生命の約束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:31.07,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}止まらない進化が呼び覚ましてく　命の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:36.28,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}狂おしく飢えて　乾いた心だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:44.25,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}溢れる狂気も纏って　今立ち上がる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.25,0:01:45.00,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}Shout and roar！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:50.21,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}解き放つ咆哮　その闇を震わす
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:53.00,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}恐れなく踏み出した
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:55.71,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}その一歩が痛みを呼ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.71,0:01:58.59,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}鋭く刺さる罪は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:01.39,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}この世界に潜む
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:05.56,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}真実はその嘘を飲み込んだままで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:08.69,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}全てを見つめてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:51.82,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}混雜交織的叫喊打破寂靜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:54.61,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}敏感的野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:57.45,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}唯有勝者擁有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:01:00.28,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}打磨出鋒利的獠牙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.37,0:01:03.08,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}緊咬不放的瘋狂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:07.25,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}去迎敵嗎？戰鬥不需要理由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:10.13,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}唯獨追求強大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:25.43,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}螺旋維繫的生命的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:31.07,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}無止境的進化喚起生命的顫動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:36.28,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}瘋狂地渴望 只剩乾枯的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:44.25,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}滿溢的瘋狂纏身 現在站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.25,0:01:45.00,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}叫喊和咆哮！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:50.21,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}被解放的咆哮 使黑暗顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:53.00,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}無所畏懼的邁出一步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:55.71,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}哪怕這一步會招致疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.71,0:01:58.59,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}銳利地刺入的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:01.39,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}潛伏在這個世界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:05.56,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}真實吞嚥下這份謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:08.69,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}卻注視著一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:13.56,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}欲望のままにあれ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.72,0:22:16.02,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}どうにでもなれなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.18,0:22:18.56,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}可愛いもの見たさで
